{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"AnimationEvent()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/AnimationEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><em><code>AnimationEvent()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/animationName\"><code>animationName</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/elapsedTime\"><code>elapsedTime</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/pseudoElement\"><code>pseudoElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>The <code><strong>AnimationEvent()</strong></code> constructor returns a newly created <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a>, representing an event in relation with an animation.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>animationEvent</em> = new AnimationEvent(<em>type</em>, {animationName: <em>aPropertyName</em>,\n                                           elapsedTime  : <em>aFloat</em>,\n                                           pseudoElement: <em>aPseudoElementName</em>});\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<p><em>The <code>AnimationEvent()</code></em><em> constructor also inherits arguments from <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event/Event\" title=\"Event()\"><code>Event()</code></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"type\"><code>type</code></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> 代表 <code>AnimationEvent</code> 类型的名称。大小写敏感，有三个值可选：<code>'animationstart'</code>、<code>'animationend'</code> 和&nbsp;<code>'animationiteration'</code>。</dd>\n <dt id=\"animationname\"><code>animationName</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">可选</span></dt>\n <dd>A <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing the value of the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/animation-name\"><code>animation-name</code></a> CSS property associated with the transition. It defaults to <code>\"\"</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"elapsedtime\"><code>elapsedTime</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">可选</span></dt>\n <dd>A <code>float</code> giving the amount of time the animation has been running, in seconds, when this event fired, excluding any time the animation was paused. For an <code>\"animationstart\"</code> event, <code>elapsedTime</code> is <code>0.0</code> unless there was a negative value for <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-delay\">animation-delay</a></code>, in which case the event will be fired with <code>elapsedTime</code> containing&nbsp; <code>(-1 * </code><em>delay</em><code>)</code>. It defaults to <code>0.0</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"pseudoelement\"><code>pseudoElement</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">可选</span></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>, starting with <code>\"::\"</code>, containing the name of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-elements\">pseudo-element</a> the animation runs on. If the animation doesn't run on a pseudo-element but on the element, an empty string: <code>\"\"</code><code>.</code> It defaults to <code>\"\"</code>.&nbsp;</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"标准","id":"标准","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-animations/#dom-animationevent-animationevent","title":"CSS Animations Level 2"}],"query":"api.AnimationEvent.AnimationEvent"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.AnimationEvent.AnimationEvent","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/AnimationEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参考","title":"参考","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Animations/Using_CSS_animations\">Using CSS animations</a></li>\n <li>Animation-related CSS properties and at-rules: <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation\">animation</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-delay\">animation-delay</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-direction\">animation-direction</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-duration\">animation-duration</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-fill-mode\">animation-fill-mode</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-iteration-count\">animation-iteration-count</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-name\">animation-name</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-play-state\">animation-play-state</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-timing-function\">animation-timing-function</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@keyframes\">@keyframes</a></code></li>\n <li>The <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a> interface it belongs to.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"标准","id":"标准"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参考","id":"参考"}],"summary":"The AnimationEvent() constructor returns a newly created AnimationEvent, representing an event in relation with an animation.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"AnimationEvent()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"AnimationEvent()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"AnimationEvent()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"AnimationEvent()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"AnimationEvent()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"AnimationEvent.initAnimationEvent()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/animationevent/animationevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/animationevent/animationevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent","title":"AnimationEvent"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/AnimationEvent","title":"AnimationEvent()"}],"pageTitle":"AnimationEvent() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}